    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or a speck on it! I've babied this car since day one, and it's looking absolutely flawless. If you're looking for that brand-new feel without the dealership hassle, this is the one for you. Can't wait for someone to enjoy it as much as I have!",
