    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in collector-tier Laguna Seca Blue. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and optimized by a dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed with technical precision, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with high-durometer bushings, providing the visceral feedback and turn-in precision characteristic of this chassis. This is a mechanically flawless, concours-ready specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
