    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It is in truly stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, and it's been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and still has that 'new car' magic. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this beauty go to a great new home!",
      "price": 43500.0,
