    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically superlative A80 Supra Turbo in museum-grade condition. This specimen features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, maintaining its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration with flawless boost delivery and zero shaft play. Power is delivered through the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox to a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis is exceptionally tight, retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry with no bushing degradation or hydraulic leaks. Recent diagnostics confirm perfect compression across all six cylinders and a leak-down test within 2% of factory specifications. The engine bay is pristine, showing no heat cycling fatigue on plastics or hoses. Every component, from the active aero front spoiler to the instrumentation, functions with surgical precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a pure, unmolested example of Japanese grand touring excellence.",
